******
[1] Sierra Leone: 7th doctor dies of Ebola
Date: 18 Nov 2014
Source: Philly News (AP) [edited]
http://www.philly.com/philly/news/nation_world/20141118_ap_56b33081b46e4202aa9c3d714422b0e0.html


A top health official says a 7th doctor in Sierra Leone has died of Ebola. Dr. Moses Kargbo, who had been a retired medical officer in the Ministry of Health, died on Tue [16 Nov 2014] at the Hastings Ebola Treatment Center east of the capital, Freetown, where he had been receiving treatment. He had been volunteering to help fight the spread of the virus at a government hospital in the central Tonkolili district... - more

